NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
M.P., Defendant-Petitioner, In the Matter of A.P., a Minor-Respondent. C-136 September Term 2017
079059 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 16, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000556-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
